0.39.0  2014-02-08

new features
- slidingspans and history support
- genhol, a function to generate holiday regression variables
- user defined variable for the transform spec
- new diagnostical statistics
- NA handling as in R base
- inspect function with model and transformation selection, new views

enhancements
- monthplot also shows SI ratios
- summary shows some useful statistics
- easier access to X-13 .out content
- regression effects can be extracted
- checkX13 performs a test run
- various code improvements
- fewer, more structured help pages
- comprehensive list of examples from the official manual

bug fixes
- quotes in the series name do not lead to X-13 error
- support for unorthodox frequencies, e.g. 2
- spaces in folder names on windows are allowed
- regression and x11regression can be combined


